// ProjectDeliveryS142 — Sprint 142: introductionDryRun (D0093) — walked the `introduction` onboarding
// skill end-to-end on a fresh `keel init` project. Found + FIXED two real onboarding gaps: (1) the
// tracking-template had duplicate :>> id lines on 3 example items (a newcomer copying them would author
// malformed items); (2) a fresh scaffold shipped NO .tracking/actors.sysml, so the newcomer's FIRST
// recorded fact failed the actors guard (D0037). Verified the init->author->close->orient loop works on
// a fresh project. 3 pts. AUTONOMOUS (D0049).
