    verification introductionDryRunReviewGate : Test { :>> id = "63940516-2c7d-4e8f-c142-51627384c00a"; :>> title = "Sprint 142 review gate"; :>> createdAt = "2026-06-23"; :>> createdBy = "claudeOpus"; :>> method = VerificationMethod::inspect; :>> procedureText = "Diff reviewed. The dry-run earned its keep: a passive read of the skill would have missed BOTH gaps — the duplicate-id template (a copy-paste trap) and the missing actors registry (a hard blocker: a newcomer literally could not record a guard-passing fact day one). Both fixed at the source + regression-guarded in init_smoke. The init->author->close->orient loop is verified on a fresh instance, and the skill's full-ceremony step is confirmed load-bearing. Clean."; }
